# This document will serve as a dictionary for the next updates of the game

## New label dictionnary (> version 1.7 Alpha)
#Strings
Str1 : Player 1 name
Str2 : Pokemon #1
Str3 : Name of Pokemon #1's attack #1
Str4 : Name of Pokemon #1's attack #2
Str5 : Pokemon #2 name
Str6 : Name of Pokemon #2's attack #1
Str7 : Name of Pokemon #2's attack #2
Str8 : Name of enemy Pokemon
Str9: Name of the enemy Pokémon's attack #1; random function required
Str0: Name of enemy Pokémon's attack #2; random function required

#Labels
00; Exit game
0A; Enter password page
0B; Home menu
0C; Getkey of home menu
0D; Warning page (new game)
0E; Main menu (continue game)
0F; Credits
0G; Settings
0H; Set password page
0I; Getkey of warning page
0J; Introduction (new game confirmed)
0K; getkey of pokemon starter choice
0L; Magikarp page
0M; Pikachu page
0N; Rowlet page
0O; Metang page
0P; Discover forest
0Q; Fighting arena
0R; Secret Dungeon
0S; My Pokémons
0T; My bag
0U; Shop
0V; My profile
0W; Loading page + Introducing fight
0X; Discover forest
0Y; fight tutorial
0Z; Choose pokémon n°1/2 page
0θ; choosing random enemy
01; showing enemy
02; Battle menu
03; Information
04; ATK 1
05; ATK 2
06; Capture enemy
07; Quit battle
08; Use potion
09; Change pokémon
10; My pokémon
1A; Enemy pokémon info
1B; Pokémon 1 info
1C; Pokémon 2 info
1D; Battle page (player's turn)
1E; Battle page (enemy's turn)
1F; Change pokémon (when one is dead)
1G; Win page
1H; getkey (when a pokémon die ; cf lbl 1F)
1I; Lose page
1J; level up condition
1K; use pokéball
1L; use big pokéball
1M; use méga pokéball
1N; pokémon capture success
1O; Menu (pokémon capture success)
1P; Pokémon 1 has been replaced by enemy
1Q; Pokémon 2 has been replaced by enemy
1R; Confirm of throwing enemy away
1S; Throw enemy away
1T; Lose page when runing away from the battle
1U; level up page; setting ⌊PKSAV(2)


